line_1: That since They gave Things their Beginning;
line_2: And set this Whirligig a Spinning;

line_1: This book, says he, (snift, snift) has in the beginning,
line_2: (The ladies give audience to hear his opinion)

line_1: That whore we speak of i' th' beginning,
line_2: Hath some excuse to make for sinning:

line_1: What, in the very first beginning!
line_2: Your history whither are you spinning?

line_1: I came to the place where life had its beginning,
line_2: Taking root with the groves that around me were springing;
